---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="#NoMoreLyes Resources on Hair Relaxers & Cancer | Level Up" description="Level Up's #NoMoreLyes campaign resource kit linking hair relaxers to uterine cancer, fibroids and respiratory disease.">

  <!-- Hero Banner -->
  <section id="sub-page-hero-banner" class="hero-banner">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <h2 class="hero-title visually-hidden">#NoMoreLyes Relaxer Info Kit</h2>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Campaign Info Section -->
  <section class="campaign-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="campaign-layout">
        <div class="campaign-image">
          <img src="https://welevelup.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Copy-of-NoMoreLyes_FINAL-18-1-scaled-1.webp" alt="#NoMoreLyes Campaign" width="1000" height="1500" />
        </div>
        <div class="campaign-content">
          <h1 class="campaign-heading">#NoMoreLyes: Research &amp; Resources</h1>
          <h2 class="campaign-subheading">All the research and articles on the effects of hair relaxers in one place</h2>
          <div class="campaign-body">
            <p>Since the launch of Level Up's #NoMoreLyes campaign in 2021, L'Oréal – the largest global manufacturer of hair relaxers – has denied links between their products and various illnesses including uterine cancer, fibroids and respiratory disease. L'Oréal, and other manufacturers including Revlon, have argued that there isn't enough scientific evidence to prove that their hair relaxers could be harming Black women – a growing body of research from institutions like Oxford University and Boston University would suggest otherwise.</p>
            <p>We know it can be overwhelming to keep up with the emerging studies, articles, lawsuits and news on this issue, so we've compiled a list of resources in one place. We'll update the collection as we gather more information but we need your help. If you come across any research, videos, articles, podcasts or anything else about the harmful effects of hair relaxers please share them with us and we'll add them to the list!</p>
            <p>The more information we gather the harder it becomes for corporates like L'Oréal to evade accountability for the risks posed by their products.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="https://levelup.yourmovement.org/p/no-more-lyes" class="btn-petition" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SIGN THE PETITION</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Filter + Resources Grid -->
  <section class="resources-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="filter-row">
        <div class="filter-select-wrapper">
          <select class="filter-select" aria-label="Filter by category">
            <option value="toxic-chemicals">TOXIC CHEMICALS IN HAIR RELAXERS</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <div class="filter-select-wrapper">
          <select class="filter-select" aria-label="Filter by type">
            <option value="all">ALL TYPES</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <div class="filter-select-wrapper">
          <select class="filter-select" aria-label="Filter by year">
            <option value="all">ALL YEARS</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <div class="filter-select-wrapper">
          <select class="filter-select" aria-label="Filter by author">
            <option value="all">ALL AUTHORS</option>
          </select>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="resources-note">Resources are loaded dynamically. Please visit <a href="https://welevelup.org/nomorelyes-relaxer-info-kit/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">welevelup.org</a> for the full list of resources.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  :root {
    --navy: #0D0A3E;
    --lime: #CBFF32;
    --cream: #EDEBD2;
    --white: #FFFFFF;
  }

  .hero-banner {
    min-height: 500px;
    background-color: var(--navy);
    background-image: url('https://welevelup.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/NML-BOX-BANNER-2-1.webp');
    background-position: center center;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-size: cover;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1.8em 0;
  }

  .hero-inner {
    max-width: 1130px;
    width: 100%;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  .visually-hidden {
    position: absolute;
    width: 1px;
    height: 1px;
    padding: 0;
    margin: -1px;
    overflow: hidden;
    clip: rect(0,0,0,0);
    white-space: nowrap;
    border: 0;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1130px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  .campaign-section {
    background-color: var(--cream);
    padding: 5rem 0;
  }

  .campaign-layout {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row-reverse;
    gap: 40px;
    align-items: stretch;
    flex-wrap: wrap-reverse;
  }

  .campaign-image {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 220px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .campaign-image img {
    width: 100%;
    display: block;
  }

  .campaign-content {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 280px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .campaign-heading {
    font-family: 'blogh', 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 0.9em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin: 0;
    text-align: start;
  }

  .campaign-subheading {
    font-family: 'blogh', 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 0.9em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1.1em;
    text-align: start;
  }

  .campaign-body {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--navy);
  }

  .campaign-body p {
    margin: 0 0 1em;
  }

  .btn-petition {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: monospace, sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 10px 12px;
    background-color: var(--lime);
    color: var(--navy);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
    align-self: flex-start;
  }

  .btn-petition:hover,
  .btn-petition:focus {
    color: var(--cream);
  }

  .resources-section {
    padding: 5rem 0;
    background-color: var(--cream);
  }

  .filter-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .filter-select-wrapper {
    width: 100%;
  }

  .filter-select {
    width: 100%;
    background-color: var(--navy);
    color: var(--cream);
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    appearance: none;
    -webkit-appearance: none;
  }

  .resources-note {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--navy);
    padding: 20px;
    background-color: #e8e8e8;
    border: 1px solid #c4c4c4;
  }

  .resources-note a {
    color: var(--navy);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .hero-banner {
      padding: 3.5em 0;
    }

    .campaign-layout {
      flex-direction: column;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .filter-row {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .campaign-section {
      padding: 2.5rem 0;
    }

    .campaign-layout {
      padding: 0;
    }

    .resources-section {
      padding: 0;
    }

    .filter-row {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
